B.QW=s(["Labyrinth is the main quest screen. It separates active work into Daily, Main, and Side quests.","Daily quests can be scheduled across one or more weekdays. Main and Side quests stay available until cleared.","Each quest has a rank from C to SSS. Completing a quest grants rank-based XP, can level you up, and can award AP.","Completed quests now clear with a check-and-burn animation before they leave the board.","Completing at least one quest for the day starts or maintains your streak.","The drawer holds Missions, Guild, Reward Shop, Inventory, Theme, Goal doc name, History, Settings, Mail, About, and Logout."],t.s)
