B.QX=s(["Nutrition tracks the food side of the System: ingredients, recipes, shopping notes, and daily intake.","Kitchen items can be added, edited, removed, and used by recipes.","Recipes help turn saved ingredients into repeatable meal plans.","Daily logs record food intake so the app can keep nutrition history alongside your progression.","Monthly audit mail reminds you to review your body stats, but weight can be updated once per day from Status."],t.s)
