B.QM=s(["Library is a saved-link archive for anything you want to revisit.","You can add links, search them, reorder entries, edit old records, and delete what you no longer need.","Opening a link uses the in-app viewer when possible, with a fallback to the browser.","It is meant for quick access to references, anime pages, tools, trackers, school links, work links, or guides."],t.s)
