B.R1=s(["Theme lets you set separate background images for Labyrinth, Nutrition, Library, and Status.","A shared dim overlay keeps text and cards readable over custom images.","Theme images are bound to the signed-in Firebase account, so Google and anonymous profiles stay separate on the same device.","On web builds, the image picker opens from the Theme menu item in the Labyrinth drawer."],t.s)
